All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
HtmlScanner
The class HtmlScanner is used to create a connection to a specified URI.
HtmlScannerMain
The class HtmlScannerMain is used to run the entire program.
HttpOptions
The class HttpOptions is used to store general information used when sending a request.
MultiHtmlScanner
The class MultiHtmlScanner is used to send requests to a multitude of target URIs of the same domain.
UserAgents
The class UserAgents is an enumeration which stores an assortment of User-Agents that can be used for the headers when sending a HTTP request.
